Network Operator v26.4.0 release is ready.

Verification results: - Attached 26.4.0 test results email

Network Operator 26.4.0 documentation - https://mellanox.github.io/network-operator-docs/index.html#

Please, take a note that the release image is published to the registry:
•	Network Operator:
o	NGC: nvcr.io/nvidia/cloud-native/network-operator:v26.4.0
•	Network Operator OCP bundle:
o	nvcr.io/nvidia/cloud-native/network-operator-bundle:v26.4.0

Bug Fixes:
•	NIC configuration operator - Fix: FW reset on GB300 leads to node reboot and may prevent other devices configuration #358
•	SRIOV Operator/Spectrum-x Operator - [SPC-X] Fix: Add HW steering mode in SRIOVNetworkNodePolicy devlink params #181, #215
•	Spectrum-x Operator - Fix: Setting SRIOVNetworkPoolConfig maxUnavailable=1 to reduce impact of parallel draining all cluster nodes in with E/W NICs #211
•	Spectrum-x Operator - Fix: Set OVS bridge datatype to netdev #212
•	Spectrum-x Operator - Fix: Add rdmaDeviceName according to railTopology name to avoid setting same rdma device name on host #219
•	DOCA OFED - Fix: DTK failing over missing DMKS packages. Make --without-dkms conditional on USE_DKMS #319

netop-tools updates:
•	Add L3 switch fabric support for routed SR-IOV pod networks using nv-ipam CIDRPool.
•	Add ops/debug-switch-fabric.sh L3 gateway generation for switch-<switch>-<port>-L3.yaml artifacts.
•	Add ops/apply-switch-fabric.sh to generate dry-run switch gateway patches from switch config, global_ops_user.cfg, live CIDRPool allocations, and LLDP-discovered worker PF ports; --apply copies patches to switches and runs nv config patch/diff/apply.
